+| Copy-paste regressions | `#[regression]` tests | Dedicated `cargo test -- regression` step |
+
+If you implement only **one** of these today, make it the **contract tests for the pipeline boundaries**. That alone would have caught `parse_extern_type` returning unit, the tuple GEP hardcoded to 0, and the struct field access bug—all before they shipped.
